Cos (script event)
==================

Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game\_class) type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Returns the cosine of the given angle in degrees.

Usage
-----

*float* cos( *float* **degrees** )

Parameters
----------

-   [degrees] - The angle to calculate the cosine of.

Examples
--------

` `
`cosAng = `<font color="#0000ff">`sys`</font>`.`<font color="#ff0000">`cos`</font><font color="#000000">`(`</font><font color="#0000dd">`90`</font><font color="#000000">`)`</font>`;`

Notes
-----

This script event returns the cosine of the given angle.


